snippet.title: Hu Tao vs Maguu Kenki in 49s (Amber support) - Spiral Abyss 12-2-1
snippet.description:
So I just heard that this team gives the best DPS for Hu Tao so I tried it a few times and I'm satisfied.

Amber's Q looks to be a great support here.
This is because Amber's Q is able to overtake Kazuha's hydro infusion, therefore making Kazuha able to swirl pyro as well with his E.

Hu Tao's DPS can be hugely increased when Amber is C6 (her C6 buff party Movement Speed and increase Att 15%) and also if Amber use Elegy of the End.

Perhaps Thoma could also be a great synergy with Hu Tao (especially C6 Thoma).

#genshinimpact #spiralabyss #maguukenki #hutao #kazuha #amber
